snippet.title: Puzzle Dimension Trailer
snippet.description:
http://www.puzzledimension.com/
Puzzle Dimension is a new high-end 3D Puzzle Game. 100 twisted puzzles, audiovisuals that blend depending on progress.

Developed by Swedish indie studio Doctor Entertainment.
